This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as temporal and causal relation extraction from text. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing a framework for an integrated relation extraction system. Additionally, it may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses the use of word embeddings and training data expansion to improve the relation extraction systems. It could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper involves extracting structured information from text. Finally, it may belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the paper discusses the use of neural networks for relation extraction.
